# PDLO for a generic button UI piece (v1.0)

SECTION      | KEY             | TYPE
-------------------------------------------------------------
META         | piece_id        | ui_components/button
META         | version         | 1.0
META         | determinism     | bounded

STATE        | label           | string
STATE        | visual_state    | string
STATE        | x               | int
STATE        | y               | int
STATE        | width           | int
STATE        | height          | int
STATE        | focus_index     | int

METHOD       | set_label       | void | c:plugins/+x/set_label.+x
METHOD       | set_focus_state | void | c:plugins/+x/set_focus_state.+x

EVENT_IN     | on_click        | void
EVENT_IN     | on_focus        | void
EVENT_IN     | on_blur         | void

EVENT_OUT    | clicked         | void
EVENT_OUT    | focused         | void
EVENT_OUT    | blurred         | void
